@startuml
title Distributed Lock Auto Renew Lost / Fencing Rejected Flow

participant "业务代码" as Biz
participant "DistributedLockClient" as Client
participant "LockWatchdog" as Watchdog
participant "RedisLockProvider" as Provider
participant "Redis" as Redis
participant "LockHandle" as Handle
participant "业务数据库" as DB

Biz ->> Client: execute(lockName, autoRenew=true, callback)

Client ->> Provider: acquire()
Provider ->> Redis: EVAL acquire.lua
Redis -->> Provider: acquired, fencingToken=100

Client ->> Watchdog: start(handle)

note over Client, Watchdog
JVM 长 GC 或网络抖动，续期错过
end note

Watchdog ->> Provider: renew(handle)
Provider ->> Redis: EVAL renew.lua
Redis -->> Provider: NOT_FOUND or NOT_OWNER
Provider -->> Watchdog: renew failed

Watchdog ->> Handle: markLostOnce()

Biz ->> Handle: assertHeld()
Handle -->> Biz: throws LockLostException

alt 业务没有提前 assertHeld
    Biz ->> DB: update with fencingToken=100
    DB -->> Biz: update count = 0
    Biz -->> Client: throw FencingTokenRejectedException
end

Client -->> Biz: LockResult(LOCK_LOST or FENCING_REJECTED, acquired=true)

@enduml